headline: Omnicom Named World's Most Effective Holding Group in 2024 Effie Index®
summary: Omnicom (NYSE: OMC) has been named the Most Effective Holding Group in the 2024 Effie Index®, the leading global ranking of marketing effectiveness. This marks the second year in a row -- and third time in four years -- that Omnicom has earned this top honor.
